room_title: Escape room "Space Quest " by Escape St. Pete in Tampa
room_description:
You are the Captain and crew of the USS Burg and while on a mission of peaceful exploration your navigational guidance system fails and you inadvertently cross into hostile alien territory. 

Before you can react the ship is under attack, your engines have failed and your transporter is disabled.

You start to feel strange and then everything goes black.

Can you save the ship and crew before it's too late?
